The input array `scores` is not null.
The input array `edges` is not null.
The length of the input array `scores` is equal to `n`.
The length of the input array `edges` is not greater than `5 * 10^4`.
Each element in the input array `edges` is an array of length - The values in the input array `edges` are valid node indices, i.e., between `0` and `n - 1`.
The values in the input array `scores` are valid scores, i.e., between `1` and `10^8`.
